"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-26-joa-boss-expects-greatest-olympics-ever-games-open-today\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France - President of Jamaica Olympic Association (JOA)Christopher Samuda says this year's Games will be one of the greatest ever as the city of Paris prepares to host the opening ceremony today - one of the biggest open-air shows on Earth.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999912018716257, \"rank\": 7.072994056861933e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999631655, \"rank\": 3.690746780186947e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"JOA)Christopher Samuda\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Games\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest open-air shows\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"Earth\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will mark the first time the theatrical curtain-raiser for the world's biggest sporting event takes place outside a stadium.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the theatrical curtain-raiser\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest sporting event\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of the traditional parade around a stadium track, more than 9,000 of the world's top athletes will be transported by boat along six kilometres of the River Seine in a kind of sporting armada, as more than 300,000 people watch from the bridges and riverbanks while police, frogmen, and snipers stand guard.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traditional parade\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium track\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top athletes\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"boat\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"six kilometres\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"a kind\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting armada\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 300,000 people\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridges\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"riverbanks\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"frogmen\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"snipers\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"guard\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will glide down the river while dancers, pop stars, tightrope walkers, and acrobats perform daring feats on water, rooftops, bridges, and artificial islands using pontoons, floating pianos, and helicopters.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"acrobats\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"daring feats\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"rooftops\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"artificial islands\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"pontoons\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"floating pianos\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"helicopters\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As you know, the opening ceremony is going to be different from former years; this is going to be outdoors on the river.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"former years\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is going to be a remarkable scene, one that I think commends the Olympic values,\\\" said Samuda.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a remarkable scene\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic values\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"Samuda\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a scene that brings you closer to nature and all the attributes of nature - the peace, the tranquility, the vision of the sea - and it just reminds you of the former years of the Olympics when the Games were far more connected to nature,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a scene\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the peace\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"the tranquility\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the vision\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the sea\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"the former years\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samuda also said that the ceremony is expected to help unite people across the globe, and bring back many memories from former Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Samuda\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"many memories\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"former Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It brings back Olympians and stakeholders to nature on the sea, and I think it is an excellent idea.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"stakeholders\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"the sea\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"an excellent idea\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, there are concerns about security risks but, as I have always said, we cannot have those fears imprisoning the spirit of sports,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"security risks\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"those fears\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We must be able to liberate our sport to the extent that our stakeholders - both internally and externally - and those fascinated by sport can enjoy the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"our stakeholders\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having it outdoors, where we will be looking at the heavens, the Earth, and the fruits of the Earth, I think is an excellent idea,\\\" Samuda added.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heavens\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the Earth\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"the Earth\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"an excellent idea\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"Samuda\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Triple jumper Shanieka Ricketts and swimmer Josh Kirlew are the Jamaican flag-bearers.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanieka_Ricketts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shanieka Ricketts\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanieka_Ricketts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanieka_Ricketts\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9977599417112569, \"rank\": 0.002107002573587206, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 2164, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999998333939996, \"rank\": 1.665327418293504e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Samuda underscored that he is very confident the Jamaican athletes will do well at the Olympic Games because they have shown in their build-up to the Games that they are determined to succeed at the highest level.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2248, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999998333939996, \"rank\": 1.665327418293504e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Samuda\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"their build-up\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am expecting good performances in track and field.\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good performances\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I particularly like about this cadre of athletes - and I am not saying it was non-existent in previous cadres - is that there is a yearning for success and a willingness to succeed,\\\" said the JOA boss.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"score\": 0.9999999989943262, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this cadre\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"previous cadres\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"a yearning\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"a willingness\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are willing to overcome and become champions.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"champions\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no fear of the scene, no fear for the first-timers, because they have said, 'I have earned this place and I am going to do my best and make my country proud.'\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no fear\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"no fear\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"the first-timers\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"this place\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\" HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\" HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2908}]}]}"